creator: Bilendi
descriptionHtml:
Maximiles is one of the nation's favourite survey rewards programmes. Collect points when you take part in surveys online and on mobile, then spend those points on great rewards.

You can top up your points by shopping with hundreds of the world's biggest brands, by playing games, responding to emails and more.

Reward yourself by spending points on products, experiences and vouchers from great brands. Choose from a range of over 250 rewards from our catalogue. You’ll find everything from music, film and books, through to beauty products, homeware and days out.

Now with the Maximiles App, you get all the best bits of Maximiles, meaning you can collect points and get rewarded no matter where you are!

With the Maximiles App you can:
- Collect points for complete surveys
- Collect points by shopping online
- Collect points by playing games and more
- Get exclusive deals and offers
- Get rewarded for responding to ads
- Turn your points into over 250 great products

Don’t forget you can also spend your points and get rewarded on the go!
If you are not already a member then you’re missing out – Make life more rewarding with the Maximiles app.
